      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.9/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/94bde306-cadd-11e2-95b5-52540035b04c).  Ran 11 tests.  No failures.",
