        "subject": "LU-3295 ptlrpc: cleanup recovery when unregistering service",
        "message": "LU-3295 ptlrpc: cleanup recovery when unregistering service\n\nduring recovery, the last replay request will be queued for last\nreply, which causes ASSERTION(list_empty(&service->srv_active_rqbds))\nfor these queued requests is not known for the service.\n\nChange-Id: I0fcfd3d25cabad412f4b826ad06da46387538a1a\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@intel.com>\n"
      },
